#: pisi/cli/delta.py:14
msgid ""
"Creates delta packages\n"
"\n"
"Usages: delta oldpackage1 oldpackage2 ...  newpackage\n"
"        delta -t newpackage oldpackage1 oldpackage2 ...\n"
"\n"
"Delta command finds the changed files between the given\n"
"packages by comparing the sha1sum of files and creates\n"
"a delta package with the changed files.\n"
msgstr ""
"Cria pacotes delta\n"
"\n"
"Usos: delta pacoteantigo1 pacoteantigo2 ... novopacote\n"
"        delta -t novopacote pacoteantigo1 pacoteantigo2 ...\n"
"\n"
"O comando delta localiza os arquivos alterados entre os pacotes\n"
"fornecidos, comparando o sha1sum dos arquivos e cria um pacote\n"
"delta com os arquivos alterados.\n"

